Options Menu
Right click on app-> New-> Android Resource File
File Name: optionmenus
Resource Type: Menu
Directory Name: menu
Click OK
This creates menu folder under /res folder and menu.xml file under menu folder
Drag 5 MenuItems under menu and set their ID and Title appropriately

Similarly make menu file popupMenu.xml having the following menus
Cut
Copy
paste


In MainActivity.kt file press Ctrl+O and override the functions onCreateOptionsMenu,
onOptionsItemSelected, onCreateContextMenu and onContextItemSelected


Go to activity_main.xml -> Palette ->Legacy -> Drag list view to Linear Layout
Go to mainActivity.kt

Go to strings.xml for creating arrays 
Go to listview -> Select the right button on entries -> pick a resource ->Fruits
